race.comment: CAPE DOCTOR (1) turned in a much improved effort last start dropping back to this grade, finishing 1.5L off the winner as the race favourite. He ended up further back than anticipated there and hopefully he can take closer order this time around. The one to beat on his recent efforts. ALBITON (3) missed by 0.2L over the 1300m journey at York when the race favourite. Tougher here, but he drops in weight and gets Faithfull in the saddle today. Comes here fresh and can play a leading role. PARC IT IN HERE (2) didn't get into the race at Northam first-up but looks better suited back to this level. The rise in trip is a big positive for him and he was competitive in similar races to this last campaign. Expecting improvement with that run under his belt. LORDGIVEMESTRENGTH (7) was outclassed at Ascot last start but this looks a better scenario for her today. Can improve. NICCY'S AFFAIR (9) jumps right up in trip now and has claims.
